 <br>
1 Ruined Cat/Wolf/Bear Pelt <br>
1 Appropriate pattern <br>
 <br>
Combined in Sewing kit, trivials at 26. <br>
 <br>
Woven Mandrake: <br>
 <br>
2 Mandrake Roots <br>
 <br>
Combined in a Sewing kit, trivials at 66. <br>
