 <br>
1 Small Brick of Ore <br>
1 Flask of Water <br>
File <br>
 <br>
Combined in a forge, trivials at 37. <br>
 <br>
Now, again, lots of choices, but I personally swear by greyhopper armor as the next step. You get the hides in Marus Seru off easy mobs, which always drop either the hide you need, or a low quality rockhopper hide you can use for leather paddings. This is why its good to work multiple skills at once, to make efficient use of farming time. Don't forget the bazaar, as you don't need more than 2 stacks of hides (and that's with horrible luck, more like one stack) and these hides are usually very cheap. <br>
 <br>
