 <br>
1 Greyhopped Hide <br>
1 Mask Pattern <br>
 <br>
Combined in a sewing kit, trivials at 88. <br>
 <br>
Greyhopper Tunic: <br>
 <br>
2 Greyhopper Hide <br>
1 Tunic Pattern <br>
 <br>
Combined in a sewing kit, trivials at 95. <br>
 <br>
